            *Long* The Ranger's Plight</span></td>
          <td valign="top" nowrap><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=395&amp;sid=4d741bb18a4c86d1f0f386f5aac00e46"><img src="templates/ezHyperShadow/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>  
